sparql_query_kg2:
 Given the information provided, here is the SPARQL query for DBpedia to get all actors starring in movies directed by William Shatner:

```sparql
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE {
  ?movie rdf:type dbo:Film ;
         dbo:director res:William_Shatner ;
         dbo:starring ?uri .
}
```

This query will retrieve all distinct actors (`?uri`) who starred in movies (`?movie`) directed by William Shatner. The mappings provided in the Entity and Relation Mapping (ER2) are used to translate the Wikidata query into the DBpedia query.

