sparql_query_kg2:
 Based on the provided context and the entity and relation mapping (ER2), here is the SPARQL query for KG2 (DBpedia) to determine how many films Leonardo DiCaprio starred in:

```sparql
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>

SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) AS ?c) WHERE {
  ?uri a dbo:Film ;
       dbo:starring res:Leonardo_DiCaprio .
}
```

